# "Brave Software" is a brand name.
compare-brave-just-like-the-firefox-browser = 就像{ -brand-name-firefox }瀏覽器一樣， { -brand-name-brave }瀏覽器是免費的開放源代碼，專注於保護用戶的隱私。 { -brand-name-brave }在瀏覽器領域相對較新：其製造商{ -brand-name-brave }軟件於2016年1月首次亮相。在本文中，我們將在三個類別中比較我們的{ -brand-name-firefox }瀏覽器和{ -brand-name-brave }瀏覽器：隱私，實用程序和可移植性。

# To "piggy-back" means to ride on someone's back or shoulders, and here means that open source software builds upon the work of others.
# Variables:
#   $opera (string) - link to /firefox/browsers/compare/opera/ with additional attributes for analytics
